Privacy Policy for Securify App

Effective Date: December 10, 2024

This Privacy Policy describes how Securify, a password and credit/debit card manager mobile application ("the App"), collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you use the App. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using the App.

1. Information We Collect:

a. Personal Information:

    Name
    Email address
    Mobile number

b. Sensitive Information:

    Passwords of social accounts
    Credit/debit card information (card number, card holder name, expiry date, CVV)

2. How We Use Your Information:

a. Providing Services:

    Managing and storing passwords and credit/debit card information securely.
    Facilitating easy access to your stored information.

b. Communication:

    Sending important notices, updates, and relevant information about the App.

c. Improvement of Services:

    Analyzing usage patterns to enhance the functionality and features of the App.

3. Information Security:

a. We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal and sensitive information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

b. Passwords and credit/debit card information are stored in an encrypted format to ensure maximum security.

4. Information Sharing:

a. We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent.

b. Your information may be disclosed to trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating the App and conducting our business, as long as they agree to keep this information confidential.

5. Your Choices:

a. You have the option to review, edit, or delete your personal information within the App.

b. You may opt-out of receiving non-essential communications from us.

6. Contact Information:

For any inquiries or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: 1pfchouhan@gmail.com

7. App Ownership:

Securify is owned and operated by:

    Owner: Prince Fahad
    Owner Type: Individual

8. Changes to this Privacy Policy:

We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Privacy Policy on the App.

By using the App, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this Privacy Policy, please do not use the App.

Last Updated: December 10, 2024
